OpenVMS V8.2
 Alpha
 VMS82A_MUP-V0200

OpenVMS V7.3-2
 Alpha
 VMS732_MUP-V0300

Note: If the ACME_SERVER is running, after installing this patch restart the
ACME_SERVER process by the command:

$ SET SERVER ACME_SERVER /RESTART

